{"TopicId":189319,"ForumId":32,"TopicTitle":"I do miss No head lights on me space walks","CreatedByName":"Boris Kerball","CreatedById":200845,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-10-26T21:20:23Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Boris Kerball","CreatedById":200845,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-10-26T21:20:23Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhat happened to the ( L ) button/ lights\u00A0 since 1.8 no lights on helmets ?? any one else. will it be fixed or is this the game till KSP 2, I dont mind,\u00A0 the game is not the same since I lost docking camera the only real realistic thing in the hole game, Still seeing real camera footage on the news, of docking to space station, KSP docking from\u00A0 3rd person view, kills it for me. Still looking forward to ksp 2.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"klgraham1013","CreatedById":105132,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-10-26T23:41:12Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223695267\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022189319\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221572124823\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022200845\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Boris Kerball\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 hours ago, Boris Kerball said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhat happened to the ( L ) button/ lights\u00A0 since 1.8 no lights on helmets ??\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI hope you\u0027re kidding.\u00A0 I\u0027ve avoided 1.8 because you should always avoid a x.x.0 Squad release.\u00A0 This seems like an odd thing to remove.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Natokerbal","CreatedById":171505,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-10-26T23:52:54Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt\u0027s part of the lights action group which I believe is Now U.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Pecan","CreatedById":96332,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-10-26T23:54:06Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nU know that you press the key for lights in the vehicles?\u00A0 U might like to try that one on EVA.\u00A0 It changed before 1.8\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"jimmymcgoochie","CreatedById":199902,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-10-28T17:44:18Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nUm, try the lights button to the right of the altimeter? Alternatively try actually looking at your settings to find the relevant key binds...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"fulgur","CreatedById":195204,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-10-28T18:31:50Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI always thought that [L] was not used for lights as it\u0027s part of \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Reaction Control System\u0022\u003ERCS\u003C/abbr\u003E translation, [H] [N] \u003Cem\u003E [J] [K] [L], and so \u003C/em\u003E\u003Cem\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022text-decoration:underline;\u0022\u003E is for lights. Been that way for a while:\n\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/em\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cem\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022text-decoration:underline;\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/em\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cem\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022text-decoration:underline;\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/em\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u00220cWkCZm.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002275.00\u0022 height=\u0022720\u0022 width=\u0022960\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/0cWkCZm.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cem\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022text-decoration:underline;\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/em\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cem\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022text-decoration:underline;\u0022\u003E\nFrom \u003C/span\u003E\u003C/em\u003E\u003Cem\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022text-decoration:underline;\u0022\u003EEve\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/em\u003E\u003Cem\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022text-decoration:underline;\u0022\u003E: Order Zero, which was begun in \